name: swmm5
upstream: US EPA Stormwater Management Model (SWMM)
upstream-repo: https://github.com/USEPA/Stormwater-Management-Model
branch: develop
version: 5.2.4 (VERSION 52004, src/solver/consts.h)
extracted-from: Stormwater-Management-Model-develop/ (local checkout at repo root)
extracted-on: 2026-06-12
extracted-scope: src/solver/ (complete solver library incl. include/swmm5.h public API)
vendored-to: extern/swmm5/src/solver/
license: Public Domain (US EPA work; see third_party/licenses/swmm5-LICENSE-NOTE.md)
patches: none (see third_party/patches/)
build: cmake/third_party/swmm.cmake builds static lib target scau_extern_swmm5;
       upstream src/solver/CMakeLists.txt is retained for reference only and is NOT used.
abi-boundary: only libs/coupling/drainage/src/*.cpp may include swmm5.h; no public
              header or DTO may expose SWMM types (project-layout-design.md §4 firewall).
